ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#46: FILE: arch/ppc/platforms/pplus.c:362:
+	if ((dev = pci_get_device(PCI_VENDOR_ID_VIA,

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

